  (text "NOTES" (at 12 208 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27) (bold yes)))
    (uuid "3ebd2ecc-83d7-4424-a263-7fbe2f26596f"))
  (text "1. MCP73871-2AA/ML: 4.20V charge voltage (standard Li-Ion). CE pin HIGH = charging enabled." (at 12 215 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.0 1.0)))
    (uuid "ffd7ca80-6197-4a87-af93-e0b37c3f5766"))
  (text "   SEL1=SEL2=GND selects USB as power source (vs. AC adapter input)." (at 12 220 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.0 1.0)))
    (uuid "5708bfbb-67c5-42de-8540-804133536577"))
  (text "2. TPS63020: VIN range 1.8V-5.5V. VSYS from MCP73871 = 3.5-5.1V (USB) or 3.0-4.2V (battery)." (at 12 228 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.0 1.0)))
    (uuid "bac1d87e-ab4c-411a-bf81-a87b306b0940"))
  (text "   Buck-boost maintains 3.3V across full LiPo discharge curve without drooping." (at 12 233 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.0 1.0)))
    (uuid "1b64df1f-d15e-4cb4-824e-ba564814f878"))
  (text "3. Charge current: Iprog = 1000V / (RPROG * 500) = 1000/(2000*500) = 1mA... see MCP73871 datasheet." (at 12 241 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.0 1.0)))
    (uuid "113d2453-3e85-4fbc-a9a0-6e3ec581816b"))
  (text "   Correct formula: Iprog(mA) = 1000/Rprog(kΩ). Rprog=2kΩ → 500mA charge rate." (at 12 246 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.0 1.0)))
    (uuid "77db742d-a1a3-4799-925c-6288c79632c3"))
  (text "4. USB-C CC1/CC2 resistors: 5.1kΩ each to GND. Identifies device as USB-C sink, no USB-PD negotiation." (at 12 254 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.0 1.0)))
    (uuid "a910429e-9a55-48d2-9edd-fa349d725ac7"))
  (text "5. VBAT protected by MCP73871 internal protection. Add external polyfuse on VBAT line if desired." (at 12 259 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.0 1.0)))
    (uuid "bb6bcd5f-6ec3-4332-a9df-ed44bf31c515"))

